      "dct:title": {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Parking occupancy City of Frauenfeld"
      },
      "dct:description": {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "The dataset includes data on parking occupancy in five public parking lots in Frauenfeld, which are in municipal hands: Unteres Mätteli, Oberes Mätteli, Marktplatz (2 hours and 10 hours), Altstadt (Freie-Strasse, Bankplatz) and Zürcherstrasse (section downtown). The data is updated every 5 minutes and includes the number of occupied, unproven and free parking spaces, the total number of parking spaces and the coordinates of the respective parking space. The data is part of the Smart Parking Frauenfeld pilot project. With the help of cameras and artificial intelligence, data on the parking situation in the respective parking lots is determined here.For capacity reasons, only the data for the current day can be downloaded directly via data.tg.ch. However, all data is historicalized and can be obtained as a compressed CSV file (zip file) for one month at a time via the following link:[https://ogdtg.ch/parkdaten/2024 _09 _parkdaten.csv.gz](https://ogdtg.ch/parkdaten/2024 _05 _parkdaten.csv.gz) The URL contains the desired month for one year at a time. For example, the above link can be used to obtain data for September 2024 (2024-09).The general link structure is accordingly as follows: [https://ogdtg.ch/parkdaten/YYY _MM _parkdaten.csv.gz](https://ogdtg.ch/parkdaten/YYY _MM _parkdaten.csv.gz), where YYYY denotes the year (four digits) and MM denotes the month (two digits). The data is unvalidated measurement data. The [Regio Frauenfeld App](https://regiofrauenfeld.citymobile.ch/index.php?brandid=11579&apid=1155685913) can be used to check the current parking situation on the five parking lots using real-time data.[Link\nto the desktop view of the app](https://frauenfeld.citymobile.ch/index.php?apid=2096681313)Data source: City of Frauenfeld"
      },
